    <div class="column mobile-100 desktop-66-left">
      <h1 class="title">Consumer Affairs Hearing</h1>
                        <div class="intro-text supporting-text squiggle-border-bottom">
  Consumer Affairs will be holding a hearing on August 16 at 11:30 a.m.</div>
                                        <h2 class="header-border-bottom">Discussion Topics</h2>
        <div class="body">
          <ol>
            
  <li>
  <strong>
  11:30 A.M.</strong>
  
  <p>CRYSTAL RESTAURANT/GARAGE ROOM</p>
<p>14-20 LINDEN STREET, ALLSTON</p>
<p>REQUESTS: TO AMEND EXISTING LICENSE TO ADD THE&nbsp; CATEGORY OF DISC JOCKEY.</p>
<p>APPLICANT: RUSSIAN BENEVOLENT SOCIETY</p>
<p>M.O.R.: ALEX MATOV</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;MIDWAY CAFÉ</p>
<p>&nbsp;3496 WASHINGTON STREET, JAMICA PLAIN</p>
<p>REQUESTS: TO HAVE THE CATEGORY OF JUKEBOX REMOVED FROM THEIR EXISTING LIVE ENTERTAINMENT LICENSE AND TO AMEND THE EXISTING LICENSE TO ADD THE CATEGORY OF KARAOKE.</p>
<p>APPLICANT: BROUGHTON ENTERPRISES, INC.</p>
<p>M.O.R.: JAY A. BALERNA</p>
  </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
                </div>
